description: The Tippmann CO2 Systems arrive to you tested and ready to be filled. The tank is ready for competition directly out of the box the day you receive them. The Tippmann CO2 Tanks are equipped with the Repeater Pin Valve which is the most durable pin valve in the industry. The Repeater Pin Valve boasts a recessed valve which connects easily and conveniently and is manufactured in brass with the most durable brass fittings. All Tippmann CO2 Systems are extremely reliable at every level of play. With proper care and hydro-testing every five years, our lightweight, durable aluminum cylinders will withstand a lifetime of activity. The Tippmann CO2 System has a safety purge valve installed from the factory to the highest of industry standards. Tippmann CO2 Systems are viewed as the industry standard for reliability, durability, and safety. Tippmann CO2 Systems will help you bring your game to the next level.

The Pure Energy 20-ounce CO2 tank is ideal for all levels of paintball play. Powered by Pure Energy technology, the tank ensures a consistent recharge rate while you're in the field for maximum shooting efficiency. The tank offers such features as a recessed Pure Energy repeater valve that connects easily and conveniently to your marker, a safety purge valve installed from the factory, and durable brass construction. With proper care and hydro-testing every five years, this lightweight, durable tank will withstand a lifetime of activity.
